// |  TAB  |  Q  |  W  |  E   |  R   |  T   |                   |  Y   |  U    |  I    |  O   |   P   | PIPE  |
// | SHIFT |  A  |  S  |  D   |  F   |  G   |                   |  H   |  J    |  K    |  L   |   ;   |   '   |
// |  CTRL |  Z  |  X  |  C   |  V   |  B   |  MUTE  |  |       |  N   |  M    |  ,    |  .   |   /   | NONE  |
//               | GUI | ALT  | LOWER| BKSPC|  NONE  |  | NONE  |RAISE | SPACE | ENTER | NONE |
            bindings = <
&kp ESC   &kp N1 &kp N2   &kp N3   &kp N4    &kp N5                       &kp N6     &kp N7    &kp N8    &kp N9   &kp N0   &kp BSPC
&kp TAB   &kp Q  &kp W    &kp E    &kp R     &kp T                        &kp Y      &kp U     &kp I     &kp O    &kp P    &kp PIPE
&kp LSHFT &kp A  &kp S    &kp D    &kp F     &kp G                        &kp H      &kp J     &kp K     &kp L    &kp SEMI &kp SQT
&kp LCTRL &kp Z  &kp X    &kp C    &kp V     &kp B    &kp C_MUTE &kp C_PP &kp N      &kp M     &kp COMMA &kp DOT  &kp FSLH &none
                 &kp LGUI &kp LALT &kp BSPC  &mo 1    &mo 3      &mo 1    &mo 2      &kp SPACE &kp RET   &none 
            >;

            sensor-bindings = <&inc_dec_kp C_VOL_DN C_VOL_UP &inc_dec_kp C_PREV C_NEXT>;
