&trans      &none       &none       &none       &none       &kp C_PREV                          &kp PG_UP   &none       &kp UP      &kp F11     &kp F12     &none
&trans      &kp LC(A)   &kp LC(S)   &none       &kp LC(F)   &kp C_PP                            &kp HOME    &kp LEFT    &kp DOWN    &kp RIGHT   &kp END     &none
&trans      &kp LC(Z)   &kp LC(X)   &kp LC(C)   &kp LC(V)   &kp C_NEXT  &kp C_MUTE  &none       &kp PG_DN   &none       &none       &none       &none       &none
